She emerged from the CR.  Her tall,white, sleek and slim figure stood 
out agianst the rest of the ship. She stood for a moment outside the 
ship looking around.  Her tail gracefully swaying behind her.  She 
walked down the corridoor, looking for someone to talk to.  She 
wanted to know what was happening and what had happened.
